An '''[[impala]]''' is an African antelope.
'''Impala''' may also refer to:
In '''music''': * [[IMPALA Independent Music Companies Association]], a European non-profit trade body * [[The Impalas]], an American 1950s doo-wop group * The Impalas, the original name of the girl group [[The Jewels]] * [[Impala (album)|''Impala'' (album)]], the second album by American band Songs: Ohia
'''Other uses''': * [[Chevrolet Impala]], an automobile produced by General Motors * [[Montesa]] [[Impala]], a spanish motorcycle from the 60-70's * [[1320 Impala]], an asteroid * [[Impala (DC Comics)]], a superhero in the DC Comics universe * [[Impala (Marvel Comics)]], a supervillain in the Marvel Comics universe * [[Impala RFC]], a Kenyan rugby club based in Nairobi, Kenya * [[Impalas cricket team]], representing minor South African provinces * Impala, a licensed version of the [[Aermacchi MB-326]] jet aircraft used by the South African Air Force * [[Hotel Impala]], Malabo, Equatorial Guinea * [[Cloudera Impala]], a modern SQL query engine for [[Apache Hadoop]]
==See also== *[[Impaler]]
{{disambiguation}}
